Best Practices
======================================
- Enable Scalability 
- Disposable resources instead of fixed servers
- Leverage automation
- Loose coupling (Queues, Load balances, SNS)
-  Services, not servers
- Choose the right database
- Avoid single points of failure
- Optimize for cost
- Leverage caching
- Security in layers 
======================================
Five pillars 
- Reliabilty
- Performacne efficiency
- Security
- Cost optimization
- Operational Excellence 


Reliabilty
- VPC 
- Direct Connect
- EC2
- Route 53
- ELB
- CloudWatch
- S3
- Glacier

Performance
- Auto Scaling
- Elastic Block Store
- Elastic File System
- VPC
- Elastic container service - ECS
- CloudWatch 
- RDS
- DynamoDB (NoSQL)



